It should format a basic switch/case/default/endswitch block
{% switch media.kind %}
  {% case 'image' %}
    {% include '_components/image' with { asset: media } only %}
  {% case 'video' %}
    {% include '_components/video' with { asset: media } only %}
  {% default %}
    Nothing to show
{% endswitch %}

It should handle switch inside an if block
{% if media %}
  {% switch media.kind %}
    {% case 'image' %}
      {% include '_components/image' with { asset: media } only %}
    {% case 'video' %}
      {% include '_components/video' with { asset: media } only %}
  {% endswitch %}
{% endif %}

It should format case branches with variable lookups
{% switch state %}
  {% case status.active %}
    active
  {% case status.pending %}
    pending
{% endswitch %}

It should preserve whitespace control markers
{%- switch x -%}
  {%- case 'a' -%}
    a
  {%- case 'b' -%}
    b
  {%- default -%}
    c
{%- endswitch -%}
